snippet.textDisplay:
Coke studio has been growing leaps and bounds each season. The concepts, the musicians, the singers, composers all have shown some amazing skills. Just love seeing the various forms of music and the way each one is innovating. Even though we have had only 5 episodes here are my top 10 songs for coke studio season 9 till now.

1) Afreen Afreen - episode 2
2) Jhalliya - episode 5
3) Janay na tu - episode 1
4) Aaja re moray Saiyan - episode 1
5) Udi jaa - episode 4
6) Ala baali - episode 4
7) Dilruba na Raazi - episode 3
8) Tu hi tu - episode 3
9) Paar channa de - episode 4
10) Shamaan pe gaiyaan - episode 5
